==English==

===Etymology===

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]]:/dʌm/

===Adjective===
'''dumb''' 
# Unable to [[speak]]; lacking power of speech.
# ''(Informal)'' Describing something (esp. a person) extremely stupid.
# ''(Informal)'' Describing something unintellectual.
# ''(Figurative)'' Serving to create more problems than it solves. Pointless. 

